<i>can sweet‐talk a chess piece,</i>

461
00:20:58,491 --> 00:21:00,627
<i>surely you can find</i>
<i>a way out of this mess.</i>

462
00:21:00,627 --> 00:21:01,695
<i>I caught her off‐guard.</i>

463
00:21:01,695 --> 00:21:04,130
<i>Maybe if we wait,</i>
<i>she'll make a sloppy mistake.</i>

464
00:21:04,130 --> 00:21:05,932
<i>No,</i>
<i>that might even be worse.</i>

465
00:21:05,932 --> 00:21:08,268
<i>Maybe I should hurry</i>
<i>and make the next move.</i>

466
00:21:08,268 --> 00:21:09,703
<i>Damn it, what should I do?!</i>

467
00:21:09,703 --> 00:21:11,337
<i>I royally screwed</i>
<i>the pooch on this one.</i>

468
00:21:11,337 --> 00:21:13,473
<i>How the hell</i>
<i>am I gonna fix this?!</i>

469
00:21:14,675 --> 00:21:15,876
Sora.

470
00:21:16,743 --> 00:21:17,678
Shiro?

471
00:21:18,912 --> 00:21:20,947
The two of us are Blank.

472
00:21:20,947 --> 00:21:23,684
We'll... be... fine.

473
00:21:26,587 --> 00:21:28,589
Kurami:
<i>Stay strong.</i>
<i>Don't back down.</i>

474
00:21:28,589 --> 00:21:30,791
Now, knight,
I want you to advance

475
00:21:30,791 --> 00:21:32,526
and eliminate
that traitor Queen!

476
00:21:32,526 --> 00:21:33,860
Both:
That's it!

477
00:21:35,328 --> 00:21:37,898
What's wrong?
Come on, move it!

478
00:21:54,114 --> 00:21:55,982
( gasps )
Sora:
<i>Jackpot!</i>

479
00:21:55,982 --> 00:21:57,518
<i>This is how we're gonna win.</i>

480
00:21:57,518 --> 00:21:59,886
Shiro, you focus
on commanding the army.

481
00:21:59,886 --> 00:22:02,923
Keep them moving
so we don't get brainwashed.

482
00:22:02,923 --> 00:22:05,626
Piece... of... cake!

483
00:22:05,626 --> 00:22:07,227
You finally have a plan?

484
00:22:07,227 --> 00:22:09,896
Listen up, Steph,
you don't always

485
00:22:09,896 --> 00:22:12,699
have to lift your sword
to fight a battle, understand?

486
00:22:12,699 --> 00:22:13,800
Huh?

487
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:16,537
There's always
more than one way...

488
00:22:17,203 --> 00:22:19,005
...to win a game!

489
00:22:21,074 --> 00:22:24,811
<i>( theme song plays )</i>

490
00:23:50,631 --> 00:23:52,432
Sora:
<i>(wheezing)</i>
<i>Must I talk like this</i>

491
00:23:52,432 --> 00:23:54,568
<i>if I'm going to be king?</i>

